indicators.name: [CONFIG] % Reporting Completness - DTH
indicators.description: Number of malaria deaths reported by health facilities (public, private and NGO) divided by total number of health facilities expected to report
indicators.denominatorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports expected to report Deaths
indicators.numeratorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports recieved Deaths

indicators.name: [CONFIG] % Reporting Completness - IPD
indicators.description: Number of inpatient malaria cases reported by health facilities (public, private and NGO) divided by total number of health facilities expected to report
indicators.denominatorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports expected to report Inpatient
indicators.numeratorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports recieved Inpatient

indicators.name: [CONFIG] % Reporting Completness - OPD
indicators.description: Number of outpatient malaria cases reported by health facilities (public, private, NGO and community) divided by total number of health facilities expected to report
indicators.denominatorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports expected to report Outpatient
indicators.numeratorDescription: Number of Health Facility reports received Outpatient

indicators.name: [CONFIG] % of all-admissions/all outpatients
indicators.description: Admission rate: Number of all-cause inpatients (admissions) divided by all-cause outpatients multiplied by 100.

indicators.name: [CONFIG] % of all-deaths/all admissions
indicators.description: Case fatality rate : Number of all-cause deaths divided by all-cause deaths mulitplied by 100

indicators.name: [CONFIG] % of malaria cases with RDT
indicators.description: Number of suspected cases tested with RDT divided by total number of suspected cases tested with either microscopy or RDT multiplied by 100
indicators.denominatorDescription: Cases tested with microscopy + Cases tested with RDT

indicators.name: [CONFIG] % of suspected malaria cases tested
indicators.description: Number of suspected cases tested with either microscopy or RDT divided by total number of suspected cases multiplied by 100
indicators.denominatorDescription: Cases tested with microscopy + Cases tested with RDT

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Annual blood examination rate (ABER)
indicators.description: The number of people receiving a parasitological test for malaria per unit population per year
indicators.numeratorDescription: Cases tested with microscopy + Cases tested with RDT

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Case fatality rate (malaria admissions)
indicators.description: Malaria case fatality rate (inpatient): number of malaria deaths divided by malaria admissions mutiplied by 100

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Case fatality rate (malaria outpatients)
indicators.description: Malaria case fatality rate (outpatient): number of malaria admissions divided by total number of outpatient malaria cases mutiplied by 100

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Confirmed malaria cases
indicators.description: Cases confirmed as positive with microscopy and/or RDT

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Inpatient malaria cases
indicators.description: Admissions or hospitalization in health facility confirmed as malaria excluding admissions of pregnant women for delivery

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Malaria cases positive with microscopy
indicators.description: Cases confirmed as positive with microscopy

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Malaria cases tested with RDT
indicators.description: Suspected cases tested with malaria rapid diagnostic test (RDT)

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Malaria cases tested with microscopy
indicators.description: Suspected cases tested with malaria microscopy

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Malaria deaths
indicators.description: Deaths in health facility due to malaria

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Non malaria deaths
indicators.description: All deaths except malaria (all-cause deaths minus malaria deaths)

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Non-malaria outpatient cases
indicators.description: All outpatient cases except malaria (all-cause outpatient cases minus malaria cases)
indicators.numeratorDescription: All cause cases OPD - OPD Mal cases

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Proportion of malaria IPD
indicators.description: Malaria as a proportion of all-cause inpatient cases (admissions or hospitalizations)

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Proportion of malaria OPD cases
indicators.description: Malaria as a proportion of all-cause outpatient consultations

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Proportion of malaria deaths
indicators.description: Malaria as a proportion of all-cause deaths

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Ratio of admissions
indicators.description: Number of all-cause admissions (inpatients) per person per year. Number of all-cause consultations in a year divided by mid-year population

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Ratio of consultations
indicators.description: Number of consultations per person per year. Number of all-cause consultations in a year divided by mid-year population

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Slide positivity rate (microscopy)
indicators.description: Number of malaria microscopy positive cases divided by total microcopy tests multiplied by 100

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Test positivity rate (RDT)
indicators.description: Number of malaria RDT positive cases divided by total RDT tests multiplied by 101

indicators.name: [CONFIG] Total malaria cases (confirmed+presumed)
indicators.description: Total number of cases reported as malaria (confirmed with either microscopy or RDT, and presumed clinically as malaria in absence of diagnosis)
